This package contains adapters which are in the framework.

Class Summary
AdapterBoolean Adapter for Boolean.
AdapterCsv<T> Class to extend for all Adapter for CSV.
AdapterDate Adapter for java.util.Date

AdapterDouble Adapter for Double

French : Adapteur pour les Double.
AdapterInteger Adapter for Integer

French : Adapteur pour les Integer.
AdapterString Adapter for String, default adapter which do nothing.
AdapterTime Adapter for Time in format "HH:MI".
 

Package fr.ybo.csvengine.adapter Description

This package contains adapters which are in the framework.
It's possible to create others, you must extends the class AdapterCsv.

French : Package contennant les Adapter fournis par le moteur.
Il est possible d'en créer des spécifiques en étendant la classe AdapterCsv.
